Cell["\<\
Drawing the five stages at one glance -- 128 crossings raw, 119 after \
Reidemeister I, 45 after I+II, 18 after all local moves, and the 6-crossing \
minimal diagram from the full pipeline:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"20624a10-6380-4547-bf99-84b821437700"],

