Cell["\<\
The local tiers are diagnostic, not a cheaper substitute for the pipeline: \
Haken's 141-crossing Gordian unknot has no local moves and no reroutes \
available at all, so every level below the full pipeline returns it untouched:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"0b2ec985-a9b7-4034-8fe7-f6459b22d16f"],

